WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: ar

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:47.520
بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ 
Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
in the name of Allah, Most Gracious, Most Merciful.

00:00:49.280 --> 00:01:05.680
1. إِنَّا أَعْطَيْنَاكَ الْكَوْثَرَ 
Innaaa a'tainaa kal kauthar
To thee have We granted the Fount (of Abundance).

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:23.280
2. فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ 
Fasalli li rabbika wanhar
Therefore to thy Lord turn in Prayer and Sacrifice.

00:01:23.800 --> 00:01:43.620
3. إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ 
Inna shaani'aka huwal abtar
For he who hateth thee, he will be cut off (from Future Hope).

00:01:46.725 --> 00:01:48.885
Thank you for watching

